# Testing & Quality Assurance Rules

## Test Coverage
- All new code must have unit and integration tests.
- Maintain at least 80% test coverage for all code.

## Tools
- Use Pytest + HTTPX for backend tests.
- Use Vitest + Testing Library for frontend tests.
- Use Playwright for E2E tests.

## Requirements
- All tests must pass before merging to main.
- All test files must be organized by domain and feature.

## Documentation
- All test cases must have clear docstrings or comments explaining their purpose.



